            <scopecontent id="aspace_e176db6dfc4e913a7104ba068f9c32c5">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Posters from concerts and recitals including "Collegium Orchestra, Donald Currier, Gustav Meier" at Sprague Memorial Hall; "Piano Concert met Donald Currier" at Volksuniversiteit - entschede; "First Appearance in England of the American Pianist Donald Currier" in London; Donald Currier at Concertgebouw on 27 April 1950; and "Premier Recital du Pianiste Americain Donald Currier" at Salle Chopin-Pleyel, Paris on 17 April 1950.</p>
               <p>There are five posters, all of which appear to be from c. 1950-1975.</p>
